---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import BackHome from '../components/BackHome.astro';
---

<Layout title="Principles">
  <BackHome />

  <section class="content">
    <h1>Principles</h1>

    <div class="principle">
      <h2>First Principles Thinking</h2>
      <p>
        Reduce problems to their fundamental components.
        Rebuild from constraints rather than assumptions.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="principle">
      <h2>Systems Over Hacks</h2>
      <p>
        Build durable systems instead of one-off optimizations.
        Compounding > cleverness.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="principle">
      <h2>Clarity Over Complexity</h2>
      <p>
        If it can’t be explained simply, it isn’t understood deeply.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="principle">
      <h2>Long-Term Orientation</h2>
      <p>
        Optimize for skill accumulation and asymmetric upside.
      </p>
    </div>

  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
.content {
  max-width: 750px;
  margin: 6rem auto;
}

h1 {
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
}

.principle {
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
}

.principle h2 {
  font-size: 1rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
}

.principle p {
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: #3a3128;
}
</style>
